These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
There 7 different types of food: avocado, papaya, carrot, onion, pepper, pineapple, tomato
The people have 7 different hobbies: drawing, board-games, photography, baking, chess, writing, cooking
 1. the person eating avocado is between the person eating onion and the person eating tomato##2
 2. the person eating papaya is in the middle##1
 3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 4. the person eating pepper is between the person who's hobby is photography and the person who's hobby is chess##2
 5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 6. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person eating onion##1
 7. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person who's hobby is baking and the person who's hobby is photography##2
 8. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person eating tomato##1
 9. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
10. the person eating pepper is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
11. the person eating pineapple is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Food   | onion | avocado | tomato | papaya    | carrot | pepper   | pineapple    |
| Hobby         | writing  | board-games   | baking | drawing | photography   | cooking | chess |

