.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
7 different pets are kept: chinchilla, mouse, bird, hamster, horse, turtle, ferret
House: futuristic, gothic-revival, modern, cottage, cape-cod, farmhouse, wooden
1. the farmhouse house is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the bird is between the owner of the turtle and the farmhouse house##2
3. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the futuristic house##1
4. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the modern house##1
5. the owner of the mouse is in the middle##1
6. the cape-cod house is on the left of the futuristic house##1
7. the wooden house is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
8. the owner of the horse is on the left of the cottage house##1
9. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the futuristic house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Pet          | horse | bird | turtle | mouse | ferret | chinchilla      | hamster  |
| House   | farmhouse | cottage  | wooden     | modern     | cape-cod  | futuristic | gothic-revival |

