.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
House: palace, cape-cod, craftsman, modern, wooden, colonial, tower
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: spy, martial-arts, scientific, satire, sports, fantasy, romance
 1. the wooden house is on the left of the palace house##1
 2. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
 3. the person watching sports movies is the tower house##1
 4. the craftsman house is on the left of the colonial house##1
 5. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
 6. the modern house is the person watching satire movies##1
 7. the palace house is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 8. the person watching spy movies is between the person watching romance movies and the modern house##2
 9. the palace house is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
10. the cape-cod house is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| House   | tower | wooden | palace | cape-cod   | modern | craftsman | colonial |
| Movie-Genre           | sports | fantasy     | martial-arts     | scientific | satire   | spy   | romance    |

