.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  firefighter, accountant, engineer, nurse, coach, scientist, entrepreneur
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: crime, satire, martial-arts, action, epic, scientific, animation
 1. the entrepreneur is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 2. the coach is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
 3. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
 4. the coach is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
 5. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the firefighter##1
 6. the person watching action movies is between the engineer and the person watching scientific movies##2
 7. the firefighter is in the middle##1
 8. the person watching action movies is on the left of the nurse##1
 9. the accountant is the person watching satire movies##1
10. the person watching crime movies is the entrepreneur##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Job      | engineer    | coach  | nurse  | firefighter  | entrepreneur      | scientist       | accountant |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | action | scientific | animation | crime | martial-arts | satire  |

