The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: time-travel, action, zombie, documentary, spy, adventure, musical
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
2. the person watching spy movies is the russian##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is between the australian and the dutch##2
4. the indonesian is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
5. the person watching time-travel movies is in the middle##1
6. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the dutch##1
7. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
8. the person watching action movies is the american##1
9. the argentine is the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Nationality   | american      | argentine | dutch | spanish | australian      | russian      | indonesian |
| Movie-Genre     | action | adventure | musical       | time-travel | zombie | spy | documentary |

