.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-6::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: september, august, january, july, april, december, may
There are 7 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, soy-milk, lemonade, milk, water, almond-milk
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who's birthday is in april##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking water##1
4. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
6. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking milk and the person who's birthday is in september##2
7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
8. the person who's birthday is in december is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
| Birthday     | april | september | july | december | august | january     | may |
| Beverage   | soy-milk   | lemonade    | almond-milk    | milk      | juice  | iced-tea | water |

