 5. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
 7. the owner of the snake is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in august is the owner of the ferret##1
 9. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the owner of the ferret and the person who's birthday is in april##2
10. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
