City: hamburg, new-york, venice, prague, miami, london, paris
 1. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
 2. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
 3. the person traveling to london is on the far left##1
 4. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 5. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 6. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the person who's hobby is baking and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
 7. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
 8. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 9. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
10. the person who's hobby is hiking is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is reading##2
11. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4     |         5          |     6      |     7     |
| Hobby   | singing  | woodworking   | reading         | hiking     | rock-climbing              | collecting    | baking     |
| City        | london | new-york | miami | prague | paris | hamburg | venice |

