1. the person driving the airplane is the aristoff-smoker##1
2. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
3. the person driving the car is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
4. the person driving the airplane is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person driving the subway##2
5. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the car##1
6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far right##1
7. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
8. the bolivar-smoker is between the pall-mall-smoker and the person driving the airplane##2
9. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |    5    |      6      |    7    |
| Cigar   | blend  | alhambra       | vegafina         | pall-mall         | bolivar   | aristoff        | baccarat |
| Transport      | snowmobile | car | skateboard | trike | subway | airplane | jet-ski  |

