 1. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
 2. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
 3. the person playing billiard is the person who growsdaisy##1
 4. the person playing billiard is on the far left##1
 5. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
 6. the person who growslily is the person playing canasta##1
 7. the person playing go is the person who growszinnia##1
 8. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
 9. the person playing whist is between the person playing snooker and the person who growslily##2
10. the person playing go is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |   3   |   4    |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| Game   | billiard   | poker | scrabble | go   | snooker   | whist     | canasta  |
